1
00:01:26,280 --> 00:01:27,200
Xu Zhinian,

2
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:31,610
do you know how much trouble you've caused this time?

3
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,039
Uncle Hu.

4
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,560
Constable Xu.

5
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:45,840
Miss Hu,

6
00:01:46,520 --> 00:01:48,920
I have already sent someone to escort her back.

7
00:01:48,920 --> 00:01:49,759
Today,

8
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:52,170
my son has committed a terrible crime.

9
00:01:52,800 --> 00:01:55,680
I will definitely punish him severely when we get back.

10
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,539
Some other day,

11
00:01:57,160 --> 00:01:58,820
I will prepare generous gifts

12
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:00,720
and come to apologize in person.

13
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,520
No need.

14
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:03,920
Constable Xu,

15
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:05,800
there is no need for you

16
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:06,840
in our Hu family

17
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,560
to shed crocodile tears.

18
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:11,840
From now on, no one from the Xu family

19
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:14,460
is allowed to step foot in my Hu family again.

20
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:15,560
Please leave.

21
00:02:18,040 --> 00:02:18,640
Farewell.

22
00:02:40,760 --> 00:02:41,680
Zhinian,

23
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,530
I think I sprained my ankle.

24
00:02:43,600 --> 00:02:44,530
Let me carry you.

25
00:02:50,600 --> 00:02:52,260
If you are willing to marry me,

26
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,520
I can give up my post

27
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:56,120
and stay in Qimen from now on.

28
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,400
Linglong.

29
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,760
I made a mistake again this time.

30
00:03:18,079 --> 00:03:18,720
Linglong,

31
00:03:18,720 --> 00:03:19,560
did you know?

32
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,640
In our heaven, if you sneeze,

33
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,880
it means someone is thinking of you.

34
00:03:25,600 --> 00:03:27,040
Maybe it's my father in heaven

35
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,600
seeing how I look now,

36
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:30,600
scolding me again.

37
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:35,520
Linglong.

38
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,840
There is no one around here.

39
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:38,440
You should sit down and rest.

40
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:45,920
By the way,

41
00:03:46,240 --> 00:03:47,480
I've always wanted to ask you.

42
00:03:47,480 --> 00:03:49,720
This jade pendant can create its own illusion

43
00:03:49,720 --> 00:03:50,880
and store souls.

44
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,160
It must be a treasure.

45
00:03:52,200 --> 00:03:53,560
Where did you get it?

46
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:59,760
My father got this in his early years when he followed Master Zeng

47
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:01,160
and joined the army.

48
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:02,440
At that time, while saving civilians

49
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:04,160
and trapped by the British army,

50
00:04:04,160 --> 00:04:05,490
an old man gave it to him.

51
00:04:05,920 --> 00:04:08,040
He said this jade pendant could turn bad luck into good

52
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,300
and change one's fate.

53
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:12,160
Later, my father indeed survived against all odds.

54
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:14,820
Since then, he has treasured this jade pendant.

55
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,440
Before he passed away,

56
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,200
he left it to me.

57
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:24,600
Don't worry.

58
00:04:24,760 --> 00:04:29,220
This time, the jade pendant will definitely help you overcome this difficulty.

59
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,120
Linglong.

60
00:04:33,200 --> 00:04:34,480
You were right before.

61
00:04:34,640 --> 00:04:35,400
It seems

62
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:37,120
every time I want to help,

63
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:38,880
I end up causing you

64
00:04:38,880 --> 00:04:40,280
a lot of trouble instead.

65
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:43,730
Hurry up, sit down and rest.

66
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:54,960
Qiao Xin.

67
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:56,680
I don't blame you.

68
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:59,200
My mother asked me before.

69
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:01,620
If after I return to being a woman,

70
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:03,300
I am not as happy as before,

71
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:05,160
or as free as before,

72
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:07,450
how should I handle myself?

73
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,840
I didn't understand before.

74
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:12,160
Now I do.

75
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,760
Born into this world,

76
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:15,840
as a woman,

77
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:17,920
whatever I do,

78
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:19,380
whatever I choose,

79
00:05:20,200 --> 00:05:21,120
it is all wrong.

80
00:05:27,080 --> 00:05:28,440
Do you admit your mistake?

81
00:05:28,440 --> 00:05:29,360
Do you?

82
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,280
Do you?

83
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,320
I do not.

84
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:34,840
Good.

85
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,240
Doing this,

86
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,360
do you think

87
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,090
you have shown some manliness?

88
00:05:39,159 --> 00:05:40,400
If you were truly a man,

89
00:05:40,400 --> 00:05:42,800
you wouldn't have done such absurd things.

90
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,650
All brawn and no brains.

91
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,280
You only hurt yourself and others.

92
00:05:46,280 --> 00:05:47,600
Master, stop beating him!

93
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:48,920
I was the one who told him to go.

94
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,400
If you want to beat someone, beat me.

95
00:05:50,400 --> 00:05:51,440
Beat me.

96
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,520
My lady,

97
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,720
you are so foolish.

98
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,320
Xu Zhinian,

99
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,960
if you don't admit your mistake today,

100
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:02,490
I will beat you until you do.

101
00:06:16,640 --> 00:06:17,400
Long'er.

102
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:18,840
Mother.

103
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,290
Why are you here?

104
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:23,360
I brought you some water.

105
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:24,300
Mother,

106
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:26,400
were you seen?

107
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:28,360
No.

108
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:31,140
Even if I were, it doesn't matter.

109
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:33,040
I will kneel with you

110
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,400
so you can have some company.

111
00:06:41,880 --> 00:06:43,120
Does it hurt?

112
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:46,159
Come,

113
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:47,640
let me see.

114
00:06:52,840 --> 00:06:54,680
How did you get hurt like this?

115
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,120
Mother,

116
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:57,640
I'm fine.

117
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:06,120
It's all my fault.

118
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:09,480
You cannot marry into the Zhang family.

119
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,320
Before,

120
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,200
it was my fault

121
00:07:16,880 --> 00:07:18,320
for being too weak.

122
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:21,440
I have ruined you.

123
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,360
Long'er,

124
00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:27,520
your father is gone,

125
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,440
but you still have me.

126
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:31,720
Even if the sky falls,

127
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,800
I will hold it up for you.

128
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:37,360
Mother...

129
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,680
Rock-a-bye,

130
00:07:45,440 --> 00:07:47,360
rock-a-bye,

131
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:51,760
rowing a boat to Grandma's Bridge.

132
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,560
Mother.

133
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:59,480
Mother praises me as a good girl,

134
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:03,400
giving me a bun and a piece of cake.

135
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,880
Let me rub it for you.

136
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:31,680
I'm fine.

137
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,640
Mother...

138
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,280
Mother,

139
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,840
go back and rest early.

140
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,160
I will be fine.

141
00:09:03,920 --> 00:09:04,560
Okay.

142
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,040
Today,

143
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:16,700
I summoned the two of you here,

144
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:17,960
as you both know

145
00:09:18,520 --> 00:09:20,320
about what happened yesterday.

146
00:09:21,480 --> 00:09:22,160
Clan Elder,

147
00:09:22,640 --> 00:09:23,640
that Hu Linglong

148
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:25,930
has repeatedly caused great trouble.

149
00:09:26,520 --> 00:09:28,880
If we do not punish her severely,

150
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:31,730
it will be hard to convince the public.

151
00:09:33,280 --> 00:09:34,080
Clan Elder...

152
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,120
Clan Elder...

153
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:37,170
Li Nianci, why are you here?

154
00:09:37,520 --> 00:09:38,440
Li Nianci,

155
00:09:39,320 --> 00:09:40,520
we are currently

156
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,240
holding a meeting in the ancestral hall.

157
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,360
Why did you

158
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,600
come uninvited?

159
00:09:45,560 --> 00:09:47,320
I, Li Nianci, came here today

160
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:49,810
only for my daughter, Hu Linglong,

161
00:09:50,600 --> 00:09:52,730
to take the punishment for her crimes.

162
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,440
Li Nianci,

163
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,280
are you really willing

164
00:09:57,280 --> 00:09:59,010
to take the punishment for her?

165
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:01,880
Yes.

166
00:10:05,640 --> 00:10:06,560
Li Nianci,

167
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,840
Hu Linglong has caused

168
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,880
such a huge disaster this time.

169
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,850
What should her punishment be?

170
00:10:13,760 --> 00:10:15,360
According to the clan rules,

171
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:17,880
she should be struck from the registry,

172
00:10:17,880 --> 00:10:19,340
expelled from the family,

173
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:22,400
and never allowed to return to the Hu family again.

174
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,060
If you can spare Linglong,

175
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:25,760
I will, today,

176
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:27,160
leave the Hu family

177
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,560
and Qimen.

178
00:10:28,720 --> 00:10:30,080
I won't return to the hall alive,

179
00:10:30,080 --> 00:10:31,810
nor enter the temple when dead.

180
00:10:32,160 --> 00:10:33,760
If I break this oath,

181
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:36,250
may gods and men strike me down.

182
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:38,440
Are you...

183
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,840
serious about this?

184
00:10:41,400 --> 00:10:42,120
Elder.

185
00:10:44,320 --> 00:10:46,960
Linglong has the Hu family's blood in her veins.

186
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,320
Wenzhong is watching from heaven.

187
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,880
Please, for his sake,

188
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:51,840
give Linglong one last chance.

189
00:10:57,040 --> 00:10:58,300
Since that is the case.

190
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:58,880
Elder,

191
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:00,760
please think twice.

192
00:11:00,760 --> 00:11:02,440
Hu Wenzhong is already dead.

193
00:11:02,600 --> 00:11:03,480
This Li Nianci

194
00:11:03,480 --> 00:11:05,640
doesn't even count as a member of our Hu family,

195
00:11:05,640 --> 00:11:07,680
and she is dispensable in the house.

196
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:10,260
Besides, being struck from the registry

197
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:12,720
means nothing to her.

198
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:15,000
What do you mean by that?

199
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:17,120
In my opinion, Elder,

200
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:19,400
if Li Nianci

201
00:11:19,640 --> 00:11:21,640
wants to take the punishment for Hu Linglong,

202
00:11:21,640 --> 00:11:22,000
hmph,

203
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,920
it's not impossible.

204
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:25,400
However,

205
00:11:25,680 --> 00:11:26,440
this crime

206
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:29,170
should be judged severely,

207
00:11:30,160 --> 00:11:31,890
and the punishment increased.

208
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:32,720
Hmph.

209
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:39,520
If,

210
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:41,520
Li Nianci,

211
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:46,120
you are willing to die for Hu Linglong,

212
00:11:46,520 --> 00:11:47,040
hmph,

213
00:11:48,560 --> 00:11:50,640
I can let Hu Linglong

214
00:11:50,640 --> 00:11:52,080
stay in the Hu family.

215
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:55,100
Are you willing to trade your life

216
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,320
to let Hu Linglong

217
00:11:56,400 --> 00:11:57,800
stay in the Hu family?

218
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,200
Stepping in here today,

219
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,600
I am already prepared to die.

220
00:12:03,640 --> 00:12:05,440
If the Elder can keep his promise

221
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:07,080
to show mercy to Long'er

222
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:08,680
and not pursue past matters,

223
00:12:09,400 --> 00:12:10,640
I, Li Nianci,

224
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:13,040
am willing to kill myself here right now,

225
00:12:13,040 --> 00:12:14,520
trading my life for the promise.

226
00:12:14,520 --> 00:12:15,080
Good.

227
00:12:16,680 --> 00:12:18,540
According to the Hu family rules,

228
00:12:19,400 --> 00:12:21,060
those who commit major crimes

229
00:12:21,160 --> 00:12:22,820
should be given poisoned tea.

230
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:24,000
Elder,

231
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:24,920
you

232
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:27,690
have no objections, right?

233
00:12:32,880 --> 00:12:33,740
Just punish her

234
00:12:35,280 --> 00:12:37,000
according to the clan rules.
